# Cursor Rules Entrypoint

Focused rules live in `.cursor/rules/*.mdc`. Each file owns one concern.

Never use the em dash (`—`); use ASCII hyphen (`-`) only (see `05-ascii-punctuation.mdc`).

Priority on conflicts:
1. Explicit user instruction for the current task
2. Security/privacy and irreversible-change safeguards (00-core-security)
3. Other project rules in numeric order
